<br>
<br>
Is this selfish. Yes<br>
<br>
I am i selfish. No<br>
<br>
I am currently in the armed forced.  I have given up over 2 years away from my wife and family to defend every American's right to work hard and get what they want and/or need.  Do I want my tax dollars ( yes the military pays just as much tax as you do) to go help someone get some health care.  NO.  Thats what donations and organizations are for.  The government is here to take care of the military, interstate hiways and NATIONAL interests.  <br>
<br>
I have heard some comments on people not having health care and education.  Get a job or 2 or 3.  Dont quote me on this but i remember a tacobell sign reading HELP WANTED $10 hour plus BENEFITS.My father worked 4 jobs when my parents were young so they could &quot;spoil&quot; us with nice gifts and good food.  He also ran a 350 acre farm at night.  I wish i could get all those lost hours back with my Dad but i love him cause i know what he did for me and my 2 siblings.  To think that he would have worked all that extra time just to have it taken by the government to give to somelse is just silly. <br>
<br>
It just erks me that people say you have a RIGHT to health care.  I guess im a cold selfish bastard but i think health care is a luxury.  Did poeple for the last 10,000 years have the RIGHT to healthcare. NO. We worked hard so we could pay the medicine man to bless us or whatever the healer happened to be at the time. <br>
<br>
It all boils down to the only LAW there is in life.  <br>
<br>
The strong will SURVIVE.  Wether it be strong in mind, body or soul.  In America you will thrive.  Thats whats makes this the greatest country in the world ( although others are darn close).  <br>
<br>
GOD BLESS AMERICA!  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=silverbladetheenchanter>Silverblade the Enchanter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magi Draconis</span><br>  Posts: 2229<br> <font color=#333333>(12/3/02 5:13:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=364.topic&index=44>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.silverblades-suitcase.com/artofadreamer/3d/excaliburthumb1.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Capitolism </span><hr size=1> ..the strong will survive...<br>
